Your App Name is an iOS application designed to assist farmers and agricultural planners in optimizing crop selection based on profitability, soil type, and environmental conditions. The app calculates the net profit per hectare for various crops, taking into account factors like seed costs, watering costs under different weather conditions, and expected profits.

Crop Profitability Calculator: Compute net profit per hectare for a wide range of crops.
Environmental Condition Simulation: Adjust parameters for drought or rainy conditions to see their impact on profits.
Soil Type Matching: Recommend crops based on the soil type of the land.
Customizable Data: Update seed costs, watering costs, and profits based on current market data.
Sorting and Filtering: Sort crops by profitability, planting month, or suitability to your hardiness zone.
